218
00:08:13,961 --> 00:08:16,628
I'M SURPRISED YOU TWO MADE IT   
BACK FROM THE KINDERGARTEN      

219
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:18,363
   WITHOUT DRIVING              
  EACH OTHER CRAZY.             

220
00:08:18,365 --> 00:08:20,432
              YEAH.             

221
00:08:20,434 --> 00:08:21,867
         [ BIRD CAWING ]        
            [ SIGHS ]           

222
00:08:21,869 --> 00:08:23,101
            THIS LITTLE THING --

223
00:08:23,103 --> 00:08:24,769
           [ MUTTERING ANGRILY ]
                    AAH!        

224
00:08:26,707 --> 00:08:27,672
                    UGH.        

225
00:08:27,674 --> 00:08:29,307
HOW'S EVERYTHING GOING          
      UP THERE?                 

226
00:08:29,309 --> 00:08:30,942
                  I'M FINE.     
          THERE'S NOTHING WRONG.

227
00:08:30,944 --> 00:08:33,211
             EVERYTHING'S FINE. 
       [ MACHINERY BEEPS ]      

228
00:08:33,213 --> 00:08:35,380
                    AAH!        
           NO, NO, NO, NO! STOP!

229
00:08:35,382 --> 00:08:36,381
      PERIDOT?                  

230
00:08:36,383 --> 00:08:38,283
    [ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]    

231
00:08:38,285 --> 00:08:41,119
                    OOF!        
                 THE PANEL.     

232
00:08:43,290 --> 00:08:45,357
                    WHOA!       
     WAIT!                      

233
00:08:45,359 --> 00:08:46,691
        OOF!                    
      [ GASPS ]                 

234
00:08:46,693 --> 00:08:49,327
                 IT'S OKAY!     
               I GOT I-I-I-T!   

235
00:08:49,329 --> 00:08:51,196
                [ SCREAMING ]   

236
00:08:51,198 --> 00:08:52,664
         WHAT THE...AAH!        

237
00:08:52,666 --> 00:08:55,367
      AMETHYST!                 
    [ GRUNTING ]                

238
00:08:57,638 --> 00:08:58,904
              AAH!              

239
00:08:58,906 --> 00:09:01,072
           [ GRUNTS ]           

240
00:09:01,074 --> 00:09:03,842
         [ MUSIC ENDS ]         

241
00:09:03,844 --> 00:09:06,411
           IT'S OKAY.           
       EVERYTHING'S OKAY.       

242
00:09:06,413 --> 00:09:08,313
      IT WAS JUST A DRILL.      

243
00:09:08,315 --> 00:09:10,181
        [ LAUGHS WEAKLY ]       

244
00:09:10,183 --> 00:09:13,818
     [ COUGHS ]                 

245
00:09:16,256 --> 00:09:18,723
                UH...PERIDOT?   

246
00:09:18,725 --> 00:09:21,359
        AAH!                    
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT. I SWEAR!    

247
00:09:21,361 --> 00:09:23,061
        HEY,                    
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.           

248
00:09:23,063 --> 00:09:25,764
WE KNOW YOU DIDN'T MEAN         
 TO START THE DRILL.            

249
00:09:25,766 --> 00:09:29,134
            UH, YEAH.           
 AND THAT WAS AN ACCIDENT, TOO. 

250
00:09:30,370 --> 00:09:32,537
    WE LEAVE FOR ONE SECOND,    

251
00:09:32,539 --> 00:09:35,607
       AND EVERYTHING GOES      
         OFF THE RAILS!         

252
00:09:35,609 --> 00:09:37,742
              I BLAME THE COWS. 

253
00:09:37,744 --> 00:09:39,711
   NO, IT'S FINE.               
     IT'S FINE.                 

254
00:09:39,713 --> 00:09:42,414
WE'LL REBUILD IT STRONGER,      
       BETTER.                  

255
00:09:42,416 --> 00:09:44,182
WE'LL ADD SEATBELTS!            

256
00:09:45,185 --> 00:09:46,451
     [ GRUNTS ]                 

257
00:09:46,453 --> 00:09:47,886
         AH!                    

258
00:09:47,888 --> 00:09:50,121
         HEY, ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
           THAT WAS A CLOSE ONE.

259
00:09:50,123 --> 00:09:53,124
              IT'S A GOOD THING 
  PERIDOT WAS THERE TO SAVE YOU.

260
00:09:53,126 --> 00:09:54,292
       [ METAL CLATTERS ]       

261
00:09:54,294 --> 00:09:56,528
              YES,              
       IT IS A GOOD THING.      

262
00:09:59,132 --> 00:10:01,132
        LISTEN. I, UM...        

263
00:10:01,134 --> 00:10:03,034
  JUST SPIT IT OUT.             

264
00:10:03,036 --> 00:10:04,102
              UGH!              

265
00:10:04,104 --> 00:10:07,105
     WHY ARE YOU EARTHLINGS     
         SO DIFFICULT?!         

266
00:10:07,107 --> 00:10:09,874
       <i> LOG DATE 7-1-1-2.</i>       

267
00:10:09,876 --> 00:10:13,244
       <i> THIS ENTIRE PLANET</i>      
         <i> IS BACKWARDS.</i>         

268
00:10:13,246 --> 00:10:15,814
 <i> THERE HASN'T BEEN ONE INSTANCE</i>
      <i> OF CORRECT BEHAVIOR</i>      

269
00:10:15,816 --> 00:10:18,950
      <i> EXHIBITED BY ANY ONE</i>     
     <i> OF THESE CRYSTAL GEMS.</i>    

270
00:10:18,952 --> 00:10:22,420
        <i> I HAVE CONCLUDED</i>       
  <i> THAT THEY ARE ALL DEFECTIVE.</i> 

271
00:10:22,422 --> 00:10:24,055
      <i> BUT I AM NO BETTER.</i>      

272
00:10:24,057 --> 00:10:25,156
      <i> I FAILED MY MISSION,</i>     

273
00:10:25,158 --> 00:10:26,992
      <i> AND NOW I'M WORKING</i>      
        <i> WITH THE ENEMY,</i>        

274
00:10:26,994 --> 00:10:28,960
        <i> AND I CAN'T EVEN</i>       
        <i> GET</i> THAT<i> RIGHT.</i>        

275
00:10:28,962 --> 00:10:33,231
       <i> I HAVE APPARENTLY</i>       
 <i> "HURT" AMETHYST'S "FEELINGS,"</i> 

276
00:10:33,233 --> 00:10:34,899
    <i> WHICH WAS NOT MY INTENT.</i>   

277
00:10:34,901 --> 00:10:37,769
  <i> IF I'VE DAMAGED MY STANDING</i>  
    <i> WITH THE BEST GEM HERE,</i>    

278
00:10:37,771 --> 00:10:40,105
         <i> THEN I'VE MADE</i>        
       <i> A SERIOUS MISTAKE.</i>      

279
00:10:40,107 --> 00:10:41,506
      <i> I'M STILL LEARNING.</i>      

280
00:10:41,508 --> 00:10:43,508
     <i> I HOPE YOU UNDERSTAND.</i>    

281
00:10:43,510 --> 00:10:45,510
     <i> I WANT TO UNDERSTAND.</i>     

282
00:10:45,512 --> 00:10:47,679
           <i> I'M SORRY.</i>          

283
00:10:47,681 --> 00:10:52,350
      <i> PERIDOT, FACET FIVE.</i>     
            <i> END LOG.</i>           

284
00:10:52,352 --> 00:10:53,585
  AS YOU CAN SEE --             

285
00:10:53,587 --> 00:10:54,853
                OH, PERIDOT!    

286
00:10:54,855 --> 00:10:55,820
     [ SCOFFS ]                 

287
00:10:55,822 --> 00:10:58,023
            Amethyst:           
        HEY, UH, PERIDOT.       

288
00:10:58,025 --> 00:11:00,225
             THANKS.            

289
00:11:01,528 --> 00:11:03,528
    BUT YOU'RE STILL A NERD.    

290
00:11:03,530 --> 00:11:07,298
I'LL BE SURE TO ADD THAT        
    TO MY NOTES.                

291
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:10,368
              HOW DO YOU FEEL?  

292
00:11:10,370 --> 00:11:12,070
        BIG.                    

293
00:11:16,043 --> 00:11:19,177
      [ SOFT MUSIC PLAYS ]      

294
00:11:32,292 --> 00:11:34,759
           [ SNORING ]          

295
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:41,332
               MM.              

296
00:11:41,334 --> 00:11:42,467
                   STEVEN!      

297
00:11:42,469 --> 00:11:43,501
  [ GASPS ] GARNET!             

298
00:11:43,503 --> 00:11:44,803
IS IT MORNING ALREADY?          

299
00:11:44,805 --> 00:11:46,838
               IT'S MIDNIGHT.   
         HAPPY BIRTHDAY, STEVEN.

300
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:49,007
      OH, MAN,                  
ARE YOU FINALLY GONNA TELL ME   

301
00:11:49,009 --> 00:11:51,810
THAT YOU'RE A FUSION            
OF THE GEMS RUBY AND SAPPHIRE   

302
00:11:51,812 --> 00:11:52,911
 LIKE YOU PROMISED?             

303
00:11:52,913 --> 00:11:55,346
              YOU ALREADY KNOW  
         ABOUT ALL THAT, STEVEN.

304
00:11:55,348 --> 00:11:56,915
      [ SIGHS ]                 
     IT'S TRUE.                 

305
00:11:56,917 --> 00:11:59,984
      BUT WHAT YOU DON'T KNOW IS
HOW RUBY AND SAPPHIRE FIRST MET.

306
00:11:59,986 --> 00:12:03,088
   O-M-G! I DON'T!              

307
00:12:03,090 --> 00:12:04,856
                [ CHUCKLES ]    

308
00:12:04,858 --> 00:12:09,728
             Garnet:            
  <i> THE EARTH, 5,750 YEARS AGO.</i>  

309
00:12:09,730 --> 00:12:12,530
    <i> IT WAS A PROMISING SITE</i>    
      <i> OF A NEW GEM COLONY,</i>     

310
00:12:12,532 --> 00:12:14,566
          <i> BUT PROGRESS</i>         
       <i> WAS BEING THWARTED</i>      

311
00:12:14,568 --> 00:12:17,168
           <i> BY A SMALL</i>          
  <i> PERSISTENT GROUP OF REBELS.</i>  

312
00:12:17,170 --> 00:12:18,536
   <i> A TEAM OF DIPLOMATIC GEMS</i>   

313
00:12:18,538 --> 00:12:21,005
    <i> WERE SENT FROM HOMEWORLD</i>   
        <i> TO INVESTIGATE.</i>        

314
00:12:21,007 --> 00:12:23,675
        <i> AMONG THOSE GEMS</i>       
         <i> WAS SAPPHIRE,</i>         

315
00:12:23,677 --> 00:12:26,511
      <i> A RARE ARISTOCRATIC</i>      
         <i> HOMEWORLD GEM</i>         

316
00:12:26,513 --> 00:12:29,547
     <i> WITH THE POWER TO SEE</i>     
        <i> INTO THE FUTURE.</i>       

317
00:12:29,549 --> 00:12:31,583
        <i> ASSIGNED TO HER</i>        
      <i> WERE THREE RUBIES...</i>     

318
00:12:31,585 --> 00:12:33,218
HUP!                            
                            HUP!
              HUP!              

319
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:37,956
       <i> ...COMMON SOLDIERS</i>      
 <i> WITH A MISSION TO PROTECT HER.</i>

320
00:12:37,958 --> 00:12:40,959
   HEY, CAN'T WAIT              
FOR THOSE REBELS TO GET HERE.   

321
00:12:40,961 --> 00:12:42,093
             [ CHUCKLES ] YEAH. 

322
00:12:42,095 --> 00:12:43,528
        WHEN I SEE THOSE REBELS,

323
00:12:43,530 --> 00:12:46,197
            I'M GONNA PUNCH THEM
           RIGHT IN THEIR FACES.

324
00:12:46,199 --> 00:12:47,398
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?            

325
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:50,468
I'M GONNA PUNCH THEM            
ALL OVER THEIR BODIES,          

326
00:12:50,470 --> 00:12:52,237
AND THEN IT'LL BE OVER.         

327
00:12:52,239 --> 00:12:54,739
   -WHAT IF I JUST PUNCH YOU?   
              -OW!              

328
00:12:54,741 --> 00:12:55,740
    OH, COME ON.                

329
00:12:55,742 --> 00:12:58,409
WE'LL PUNCH THEM TOGETHER       
    WHEN WE FUSE.               

330
00:12:58,411 --> 00:13:01,946
THAT'S WHY THEY SENT,           
  UH, THREE OF US.              

331
00:13:01,948 --> 00:13:03,081
                 THREE THIS!    

332
00:13:03,083 --> 00:13:04,249
          [ ALL GASP ]          

333
00:13:04,251 --> 00:13:07,285
           OH, I, UM,           
       I'M SO SORRY, I --       

334
00:13:07,287 --> 00:13:08,887
          LET ME, UH --         

335
00:13:08,889 --> 00:13:09,954
      I'M FINE.                 

336
00:13:09,956 --> 00:13:10,922
              WHAT?             

337
00:13:10,924 --> 00:13:13,258
     IT'S OKAY.                 
IT WAS BOUND TO HAPPEN.         

338
00:13:13,260 --> 00:13:14,959
            I -- OH.            

339
00:13:14,961 --> 00:13:16,127
              OKAY.             

340
00:13:16,129 --> 00:13:19,964
NOW, PLEASE WAIT HERE.          
I MUST ATTEND TO MY DUTIES.     

341
00:13:19,966 --> 00:13:21,733
             -RIGHT.            
              -YES.             

342
00:13:23,637 --> 00:13:26,738
    <i> SAPPHIRE HAD BEEN CALLED</i>   
    <i> TO EARTH BY BLUE DIAMOND</i>   

343
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:29,741
     <i> SPECIFICALLY TO SHARE</i>     
   <i> HER VISION OF THE FUTURE.</i>   

344
00:13:29,743 --> 00:13:32,277
    MY DIAMOND, I'VE ARRIVED.   

345
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:33,745
      <i> BLUE DIAMOND SPOKE.</i>      

346
00:13:33,747 --> 00:13:36,948
       <i> "SAPPHIRE, TELL ME</i>      
    <i> WHAT WILL HAPPEN HERE."</i>    

347
00:13:36,950 --> 00:13:39,784
I FORESEE THE REBELS            
ATTACKING THE CLOUD ARENA.      

348
00:13:39,786 --> 00:13:42,420
BEFORE THEY ARE CORNERED,       
  THEY WILL DESTROY             

349
00:13:42,422 --> 00:13:44,455
 THE PHYSICAL FORMS             
   OF SEVEN GEMS,               

350
00:13:44,457 --> 00:13:47,592
INCLUDING TWO OF MY RUBY GUARDS 
     AND MYSELF.                

351
00:13:47,594 --> 00:13:49,961
IMMEDIATELY AFTER MY FORM       
    IS DESTROYED,               

352
00:13:49,963 --> 00:13:51,763
     THE REBELS                 
  WILL BE CAPTURED.             

353
00:13:51,765 --> 00:13:53,364
    THE REBELLION               
     ENDS HERE.                 

354
00:13:53,366 --> 00:13:56,634
     <i> "THANK YOU, SAPPHIRE,"</i>    
  <i> BLUE DIAMOND SAID, RELIEVED.</i> 

355
00:13:56,636 --> 00:13:58,436
 <i> "THAT'S ALL I NEEDED TO KNOW."</i>

356
00:13:58,438 --> 00:14:00,805
I LOOK FORWARD TO SPEAKING      
   WITH YOU AGAIN               

357
00:14:00,807 --> 00:14:03,641
    ONCE I REFORM               
 BACK ON HOMEWORLD.             

358
00:14:03,643 --> 00:14:06,144
         <i> SAPPHIRE KNEW</i>         
    <i> SHE WOULD BE A CASUALTY,</i>   

359
00:14:06,146 --> 00:14:07,645
    <i> BUT IT DID NOT FAZE HER.</i>   

360
00:14:07,647 --> 00:14:09,981
     <i> SHE SAW HER WHOLE LIFE</i>    
      <i> LAID OUT BEFORE HER,</i>     

361
00:14:09,983 --> 00:14:11,983
      <i> AND SHE HAD ALREADY</i>      
      <i> ACCEPTED ALL OF IT.</i>      

362
00:14:11,985 --> 00:14:15,019
WHAT A BEAUTIFUL PLACE          
 TO BUILD A COLONY.             

363
00:14:15,021 --> 00:14:18,489
I WISH I COULD HAVE SEEN        
MORE OF THIS PLANET.            

364
00:14:18,491 --> 00:14:20,291
         UH, THERE'S STILL TIME.

365
00:14:20,293 --> 00:14:22,894
THAT IS A NICE THOUGHT.         

366
00:14:22,896 --> 00:14:24,529
      BUT, NO.                  

367
00:14:24,531 --> 00:14:28,066
       Rose: BLUE DIAMOND,      
       LEAVE THIS PLANET.       

368
00:14:28,068 --> 00:14:31,002
           THIS COLONY          
     WILL NOT BE COMPLETED.     

369
00:14:31,004 --> 00:14:32,036
              IT'S THE REBELS!  

370
00:14:32,038 --> 00:14:34,672
 Ruby: WHO ARE YOU?             
  SHOW YOURSELVES!              

371
00:14:34,674 --> 00:14:38,042
    -WE ARE THE CRYSTAL GEMS.   
    -WE ARE THE CRYSTAL GEMS.   

372
00:14:38,044 --> 00:14:41,246
           <i> THE ATTACK</i>          
     <i> WAS RIGHT ON SCHEDULE.</i>    

373
00:14:41,248 --> 00:14:42,647
        [ SWORDS CLASH ]        

374
00:14:42,649 --> 00:14:43,715
              -HM?              
              -HM?              

375
00:14:43,717 --> 00:14:45,183
              -AAH!             
              -AAH!             

376
00:14:45,185 --> 00:14:46,918
      HEE-YAH!                  

377
00:14:48,255 --> 00:14:51,089
          [ SHOUTING ]          

378
00:14:51,091 --> 00:14:52,523
HUP!                            
                           YEAH!
              HUP!              

379
00:14:52,525 --> 00:14:54,859
          [ ALL SHOUT ]         

380
00:14:54,861 --> 00:14:56,361
         HA!                    

381
00:14:56,363 --> 00:14:57,862
        AAH!                    

382
00:14:57,864 --> 00:15:00,331
                [ CHUCKLES ]    

383
00:15:00,333 --> 00:15:01,399
     [ GRUNTS ]                 

384
00:15:01,401 --> 00:15:02,734
                    AAH!        

385
00:15:05,038 --> 00:15:07,772
                 [ GROANS ]     

386
00:15:07,774 --> 00:15:10,341
  THANK YOU, RUBY.              
 YOU DID YOUR BEST.             

387
00:15:10,343 --> 00:15:13,044
     <i> RUBY SUDDENLY REALIZED</i>    
      <i> WHAT SAPPHIRE MEANT.</i>     

388
00:15:13,046 --> 00:15:15,446
         <i> SHE HAD KNOWN</i>         
     <i> THAT RUBY WOULD FAIL.</i>     

389
00:15:15,448 --> 00:15:17,548
   <i> SAPPHIRE HAD ACCEPTED IT,</i>   

390
00:15:17,550 --> 00:15:20,285
  <i> BUT RUBY -- RUBY COULD NOT.</i>  

391
00:15:20,287 --> 00:15:21,653
                     NO!        

392
00:15:27,961 --> 00:15:30,261
              WHAT?             

393
00:15:32,699 --> 00:15:35,133
         [ GASPS ] WHAT?        

394
00:15:36,569 --> 00:15:39,203
       [ CROWD MURMURING ]      

395
00:15:39,205 --> 00:15:42,140
WHAT -- WHAT IS THIS?           

396
00:15:44,277 --> 00:15:46,878
              WAIT. THIS IS --  

397
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:48,246
                     HM?        

398
00:15:48,248 --> 00:15:49,547
                  LET'S GO.     

399
00:15:49,549 --> 00:15:52,583
      UH, BYE.                  

400
00:15:52,585 --> 00:15:54,118
           IS THIS --           

401
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,620
              -AH!              
              -AH!              

402
00:15:55,622 --> 00:15:58,923
  <i> THE FURIOUS CROWD CLOSED IN</i>  
   <i> AROUND RUBY AND SAPPHIRE.</i>   

403
00:15:58,925 --> 00:16:02,427
   <i> THEY HAD NEVER SEEN FUSION</i>  
<i>OF TWO DIFFERENT TYPES OF GEMS.</i> 

404
00:16:02,429 --> 00:16:03,428
        <i> "UNBELIEVABLE."</i>        

405
00:16:03,430 --> 00:16:04,429
         <i> "DISGUSTING."</i>         

406
00:16:04,431 --> 00:16:05,930
     <i> "THIS IS UNHEARD OF."</i>     

407
00:16:05,932 --> 00:16:08,633
      <i> BLUE DIAMOND'S VOICE</i>     
     <i> CUT THROUGH THE CROWD.</i>    

408
00:16:08,635 --> 00:16:10,268
     <i> "THE REBELS HAVE FLED.</i>    

409
00:16:10,270 --> 00:16:12,904
     <i> SAPPHIRE, THIS IS NOT</i>     
  <i> THE SCENARIO YOU DESCRIBED."</i> 

410
00:16:12,906 --> 00:16:16,774
         THIS IS NOT WHAT I SAW.
     I DON'T KNOW WHAT HAPPENED.

411
00:16:16,776 --> 00:16:19,610
              -I --             
         -NO, IT WAS ME.        

412
00:16:19,612 --> 00:16:21,279
 <i> "CLEARLY," SAID BLUE DIAMOND.</i> 

413
00:16:21,281 --> 00:16:24,482
       <i> "HOW DARE YOU FUSE</i>      
  <i> WITH A MEMBER OF MY COURT."</i>  

414
00:16:24,484 --> 00:16:25,616
        FORGIVE ME. I --        

415
00:16:25,618 --> 00:16:27,919
 <i> "YOU WILL BE BROKEN FOR THIS."</i>

416
00:16:29,856 --> 00:16:31,456
        WAIT!                   

417
00:16:31,458 --> 00:16:34,459
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!            

418
00:16:34,461 --> 00:16:38,696
       NOOOO!                   

419
00:16:45,472 --> 00:16:46,804
 WHY'D YOU DO THAT?             

420
00:16:46,806 --> 00:16:49,474
  I HAVE TO GET YOU             
   BACK UP THERE.               

421
00:16:49,476 --> 00:16:51,542
      THEY WERE GONNA BREAK YOU.

422
00:16:51,544 --> 00:16:55,880
     WHO CARES?                 
 THERE'S TONS OF ME.            

423
00:16:57,684 --> 00:16:58,883
                 [ GRUNTS ]     

424
00:16:58,885 --> 00:17:00,118
                      UH!       

425
00:17:02,055 --> 00:17:03,121
                    AAH!        

426
00:17:03,123 --> 00:17:05,023
 WHAT DO WE DO NOW?             

427
00:17:05,025 --> 00:17:07,959
       <i> SAPPHIRE HAD KNOWN</i>      
  <i> EVERY MOMENT OF HER LIFE --</i>  

428
00:17:07,961 --> 00:17:09,727
 <i> HOW IT WOULD HAPPEN AND WHEN.</i> 

429
00:17:09,729 --> 00:17:12,196
     <i> BUT BECAUSE OF RUBY'S</i>     
       <i> IMPULSIVE GESTURE,</i>      

430
00:17:12,198 --> 00:17:14,799
          <i> SHE SUDDENLY</i>         
   <i> JUMPED THE TRACK OF FATE.</i>   

431
00:17:14,801 --> 00:17:17,201
         <i> AND EVERYTHING</i>        
      <i> FROM THAT INSTANT ON</i>     

432
00:17:17,203 --> 00:17:18,403
       <i> WAS WRONG AND NEW.</i>      

433
00:17:18,405 --> 00:17:21,639
       <i> SHE COULDN'T SEE.</i>       
       <i> SHE COULDN'T MOVE.</i>      

434
00:17:21,641 --> 00:17:23,574
        <i> SHE WAS FROZEN.</i>        

435
00:17:23,576 --> 00:17:24,675
         AH!                    

436
00:17:24,677 --> 00:17:27,011
             WE HAVE TO GET YOU 
                OUT OF HERE.    

437
00:17:30,250 --> 00:17:31,983
                  COME ON.      

438
00:17:38,725 --> 00:17:43,161
                 ALL RIGHT,     
    THIS SHOULD BE GOOD FOR NOW.

439
00:17:43,163 --> 00:17:45,663
     THANK YOU.                 

440
00:17:48,368 --> 00:17:51,035
       [ FIRE CRACKLING ]       

441
00:17:51,037 --> 00:17:52,036
                    WHA?        

442
00:17:52,038 --> 00:17:53,371
                [ CHUCKLES ]    

443
00:17:53,373 --> 00:17:55,073
       [ FIRE CRACKLING ]       

444
00:17:55,075 --> 00:17:57,375
              WHAT KIND OF RUBY 
            AM I SUPPOSED TO BE?

445
00:17:57,377 --> 00:17:58,709
                LOOK AT THIS.   

446
00:17:58,711 --> 00:18:00,378
              IT'S ALL MY FAULT 
           YOU'RE STRANDED HERE.

447
00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:01,579
        HOW AM I GONNA SAVE YOU?

448
00:18:01,581 --> 00:18:03,114
  YOU ALREADY DID.              

449
00:18:03,116 --> 00:18:03,915
                    WHAT?       

450
00:18:03,917 --> 00:18:07,051
YOU ALREADY SAVED ME.           

451
00:18:07,053 --> 00:18:08,786
                  [ HUFFS ]     

452
00:18:27,574 --> 00:18:29,807
I'VE SEEN GEMS FUSE BEFORE,     

453
00:18:29,809 --> 00:18:33,611
  BUT I HAD NO IDEA             
THAT'S WHAT IT FELT LIKE.       

454
00:18:33,613 --> 00:18:34,946
 I ALWAYS THOUGHT --            

455
00:18:34,948 --> 00:18:37,248
  I NEVER REALIZED              
   THAT FUSION --               

456
00:18:37,250 --> 00:18:39,584
 THAT YOU DISAPPEAR             
     LIKE THAT.                 

457
00:18:39,586 --> 00:18:41,052
           IT'S NEVER LIKE THAT.

458
00:18:41,054 --> 00:18:44,388
              WHENEVER I FUSE,  
       IT'S ALWAYS JUST BEEN ME,

459
00:18:44,390 --> 00:18:45,723
                 BUT BIGGER.    

460
00:18:45,725 --> 00:18:49,760
              I-I'VE NEVER HAD  
             A THIRD EYE BEFORE.

461
00:18:49,762 --> 00:18:52,396
   I'VE NEVER HAD               
   MORE THAN ONE.               

462
00:18:52,398 --> 00:18:53,464
    IT WAS NICE.                

463
00:18:53,466 --> 00:18:56,167
                [ CHUCKLES ]    

464
00:18:56,169 --> 00:18:57,602
                    YEAH.       

465
00:18:57,604 --> 00:19:00,705
                     ♪♪         

466
00:19:01,841 --> 00:19:03,774
       Ruby and Sapphire:       
      ♪ WHERE DID WE GO? ♪      

467
00:19:03,776 --> 00:19:05,776
       ♪ WHAT DID WE DO? ♪      

468
00:19:05,778 --> 00:19:09,680
        ♪ I THINK WE MADE       
    SOMETHING ENTIRELY NEW ♪    

469
00:19:09,682 --> 00:19:11,649
   ♪ AND IT WASN'T QUITE ME ♪   

470
00:19:11,651 --> 00:19:13,818
   ♪ AND IT WASN'T QUITE YOU ♪  

471
00:19:13,820 --> 00:19:18,156
    ♪ I THINK IT WAS SOMEONE    
         ENTIRELY NEW ♪         

472
00:19:18,158 --> 00:19:21,292
                   ♪ OH ♪       

473
00:19:21,294 --> 00:19:23,094
                   ♪ UM ♪       

474
00:19:23,096 --> 00:19:26,697
            ♪ WELL, I JUST CAN'T
               STOP THINKIN' ♪  

475
00:19:26,699 --> 00:19:28,833
                   ♪ SO ♪       

476
00:19:28,835 --> 00:19:31,002
                   ♪ UM ♪       

477
00:19:31,004 --> 00:19:35,506
                ♪ DID YOU SAY   
             I WAS DIFFERENT? ♪ 

478
00:19:35,508 --> 00:19:37,375
♪ AND YOU HADN'T BEFORE? ♪      

479
00:19:37,377 --> 00:19:39,210
              ♪ OF COURSE NOT ♪ 

480
00:19:39,212 --> 00:19:41,979
     ♪ WHEN WOULD I HAVE EVER? ♪

481
00:19:41,981 --> 00:19:44,849
  ♪ I'M SO SORRY ♪              

482
00:19:44,851 --> 00:19:47,185
            ♪ NO, NO, DON'T BE ♪

483
00:19:47,187 --> 00:19:50,054
♪ AND NOW YOU'RE HERE           
      FOREVER ♪                 

484
00:19:50,056 --> 00:19:51,956
             ♪ WHAT ABOUT YOU? ♪

485
00:19:51,958 --> 00:19:53,658
 ♪ WHAT ABOUT ME? ♪             

486
00:19:53,660 --> 00:19:55,726
      ♪ WELL, YOU'RE HERE, TOO ♪

487
00:19:55,728 --> 00:19:59,063
         ♪ WE'RE HERE TOGETHER ♪

488
00:20:00,333 --> 00:20:02,099
                 [ HUMMING ]    

489
00:20:07,974 --> 00:20:10,908
        [ BOTH HUMMING ]        

490
00:20:30,597 --> 00:20:32,029
          <i> I WAS BACK.</i>          

491
00:20:32,031 --> 00:20:34,765
         <i> I WAS SOMEONE,</i>        
     <i> AND I DIDN'T KNOW WHO.</i>    

492
00:20:34,767 --> 00:20:36,267
         <i> BUT FELT LIKE</i>         

493
00:20:36,269 --> 00:20:39,770
     <i> I WAS GETTING THE HANG</i>    
    <i> OF MY STRANGE, NEW FORM.</i>   

494
00:20:39,772 --> 00:20:41,872
        <i> AND THEN I FELL.</i>       

495
00:20:41,874 --> 00:20:42,907
               AH!              

496
00:20:42,909 --> 00:20:45,109
          [ GRUNTING ]          

497
00:20:45,111 --> 00:20:46,711
               OW.              

498
00:20:46,713 --> 00:20:48,346
         AH!                    

499
00:20:48,348 --> 00:20:49,847
   DON'T HURT HER!              

500
00:20:49,849 --> 00:20:51,582
  DON'T HURT...ME?              

501
00:20:51,584 --> 00:20:55,886
         IT'S YOU -- THE FUSION.

502
00:20:55,888 --> 00:20:57,588
WE DIDN'T MEAN TO FUSE.         

503
00:20:57,590 --> 00:20:59,357
WELL, WE DID THIS TIME.         

504
00:20:59,359 --> 00:21:00,891
    WE'LL UNFUSE.               

505
00:21:00,893 --> 00:21:02,893
  WE'LL -- WE'LL --             

506
00:21:02,895 --> 00:21:06,731
               NO, NO, PLEASE.  
      I'M GLAD TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

507
00:21:06,733 --> 00:21:08,299
     <i> AND THERE THEY WERE --</i>    

508
00:21:08,301 --> 00:21:11,402
          <i> ROSE QUARTZ,</i>         
  <i> THE LEADER OF THE REBELLION</i>  

509
00:21:11,404 --> 00:21:14,405
  <i> AND HER TERRIFYING RENEGADE,</i> 
             <i> PEARL.</i>            

510
00:21:14,407 --> 00:21:16,374
 I DON'T UPSET YOU?             

511
00:21:16,376 --> 00:21:18,476
                  WHO CARES     
              ABOUT HOW<i> I</i> FEEL? 

512
00:21:18,478 --> 00:21:22,313
     HOW<i> YOU</i> FEEL IS BOUND TO BE
          MUCH MORE INTERESTING.

513
00:21:22,315 --> 00:21:23,948
     HOW I FEEL?                

514
00:21:23,950 --> 00:21:26,917
  I-I FEEL LOST...              

515
00:21:26,919 --> 00:21:28,919
    AND SCARED...               

516
00:21:28,921 --> 00:21:31,255
  AND -- AND HAPPY.             

517
00:21:31,257 --> 00:21:33,457
  WHY AM I SO SURE              
THAT I'D RATHER BE THIS         

518
00:21:33,459 --> 00:21:35,760
   THAN EVERYTHING              
I WAS SUPPOSED TO BE?           

519
00:21:35,762 --> 00:21:37,261
 AND THAT I'D RATHER            
       DO THIS                  

520
00:21:37,263 --> 00:21:39,597
   THAN EVERYTHING              
I WAS SUPPOSED TO DO?           

521
00:21:39,599 --> 00:21:40,665
                 [ LAUGHS ]     

522
00:21:40,667 --> 00:21:43,000
        WELCOME TO EARTH.       

523
00:21:43,002 --> 00:21:47,104
  CAN YOU TELL ME,              
HOW WAS RUBY ABLE TO ALTER FATE?

524
00:21:47,106 --> 00:21:50,274
  WHY WAS SAPPHIRE              
WILLING TO GIVE UP EVERYTHING?  

525
00:21:50,276 --> 00:21:51,575
     WHAT AM I?                 

526
00:21:51,577 --> 00:21:52,910
       NO MORE QUESTIONS.       

527
00:21:52,912 --> 00:21:55,746
    DON'T EVER QUESTION THIS.   

528
00:21:55,748 --> 00:21:59,016
   YOU ALREADY ARE THE ANSWER.  

529
00:22:02,955 --> 00:22:06,057
  SO, WHAT WAS IT?              

530
00:22:07,026 --> 00:22:08,626
     THE ANSWER?                

531
00:22:08,628 --> 00:22:10,361
                    LOVE.       

532
00:22:10,363 --> 00:22:11,595
        WOW.                    

533
00:22:11,597 --> 00:22:13,631
     I KNEW IT.                 

534
00:22:13,633 --> 00:22:16,000
                 SO DID IT.     

535
00:22:20,673 --> 00:22:23,207
      [ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]     

